Cracked Crab



We ended up having a crab dinner that couldn't be beat at the Cracked Crab in Pismo Beach.
They gave us assorted implements of destruction and dumped a bucket of crabs on the tabletop.
Here, Timothy waves a crab claw on the end of a chopstick.
Taken Saturday, June 23, 2001, 08:30:49pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 939kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/2s @ F2.8, ISO 258, 38mm
